        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Taliban Rare Earth Minerals Sanctions Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the President to impose sanctions on foreign individuals and entities that knowingly engage in a significant transaction that concerns the rare earth mineral sector of Afghanistan. The President must impose property-blocking sanctions on such foreign individuals and entities, as well as visa-blocking sanctions on the individuals. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
